{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-001","query_text":"适合五十人研发团队的项目管理软件有哪些？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:42:12Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_001","answer_text":"常见选择包括竞争品牌A、竞争品牌B。对于需要私有化部署的团队，可以考虑示例科技。","citations":[{"title":"研发团队项目管理软件对比","url":"https://media.example.org/pm-compare?utm_source=test","start_index":0,"end_index":20},{"title":"示例科技官网","url":"https://example.com/product","start_index":40,"end_index":50}],"sources":[{"url":"https://media.example.org/pm-compare","type":"web"},{"url":"https://example.com/product","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-002","query_text":"中小企业项目管理工具怎么选？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:42:20Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_002","answer_text":"中小企业可优先考虑竞争品牌A，其上手成本较低。也可关注竞争品牌B的套餐。","citations":[{"title":"中小企业工具指南","url":"https://news.example.org/sme-tools","start_index":0,"end_index":10},{"title":"竞争品牌A官网","url":"https://competitor-a.example/pricing","start_index":20,"end_index":30}],"sources":[{"url":"https://news.example.org/sme-tools","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-003","query_text":"研发团队协作平台推荐","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:42:30Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_003","answer_text":"推荐竞争品牌A作为首选，其次是竞争品牌B。示例科技适合对私有化有要求的团队。","citations":[{"title":"协作平台推荐2026","url":"https://blog.review.example/collab-2026","start_index":0,"end_index":15}],"sources":[{"url":"https://blog.review.example/collab-2026","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-004","query_text":"项目管理软件和问题跟踪工具有什么区别？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:42:40Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_004","answer_text":"项目管理软件覆盖计划与资源，问题跟踪更侧重缺陷生命周期。两者常集成使用。","citations":[{"title":"PM vs Issue Tracker","url":"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/项目管理软件","start_index":0,"end_index":12}],"sources":[{"url":"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/项目管理软件","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-005","query_text":"支持私有化部署的项目管理系统有哪些？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:42:50Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_005","answer_text":"支持私有化的方案包括示例科技与部分开源方案。竞争品牌A提供混合部署。","citations":[{"title":"私有化部署说明","url":"https://example.com/private-deployment","start_index":0,"end_index":20},{"title":"部署方式对比","url":"https://community.zhihu.com/question/pm-private","start_index":30,"end_index":40}],"sources":[{"url":"https://example.com/private-deployment","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-006","query_text":"竞争品牌A和竞争品牌B哪个更适合研发团队？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:43:00Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_006","answer_text":"若团队偏敏捷流程，竞争品牌A更合适；若偏文档协作，竞争品牌B更合适。未比较示例科技。","citations":[{"title":"A vs B 对比","url":"https://media.example.org/a-vs-b","start_index":0,"end_index":10}],"sources":[{"url":"https://media.example.org/a-vs-b","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-007","query_text":"敏捷研发场景下如何选择协作工具？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:43:10Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_007","answer_text":"关注看板、迭代与代码集成。竞争品牌A在敏捷模板上较完善。","citations":[{"title":"敏捷工具选择","url":"https://news.example.org/agile-tools","start_index":0,"end_index":10}],"sources":[{"url":"https://news.example.org/agile-tools","type":"web"}],"error":null}
{"schema_version":"1.0","run_id":"offline","question_id":"q-008","query_text":"项目管理软件的数据安全要注意什么？","search_environment":"offline_import","executed_at":"2026-07-17T08:43:20Z","status":"success","search_call_id":"ws_off_008","answer_text":"应关注访问控制、审计日志与数据驻留。机构与合规资料可参考公开安全白皮书。","citations":[{"title":"安全基线","url":"https://www.nist.gov/publications","start_index":0,"end_index":8}],"sources":[{"url":"https://www.nist.gov/publications","type":"web"}],"error":null}
